                  "unit_combination": "(%)"
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                "The beam energy was",
                "calibrated to +-0.1% from thick target yield curves at",
                "resonances in the reaction at proton energies of",
                "871.11 keV, EN-NRM=991.8 keV.",
                "Effective reaction energies were determined from",
                "measurements of the target thickness and of the carbon",
                "buildup by consistent Rutherford backscattering",
                "measurements and (d,p) reaction analysis of 12C,16O",
                "performed many times during the course of the",
                "experiment."
              ]
            }
